I'VE BEEN PRETTY BUSY TOO.

78
00:03:35,382 --> 00:03:38,343
CLIFF WANTS US TO SLAY
A LARP DRAGON MID-INVASION.

79
00:03:38,427 --> 00:03:40,846
(LAUGHS)
HE'S CRAZY!

80
00:03:40,929 --> 00:03:42,973
I'LL TEXT HIM BACK.

81
00:03:49,605 --> 00:03:51,565
CONNOR! YOU'RE FRIENDS
STILL COMING OVER TOMORROW?

82
00:03:51,648 --> 00:03:53,192
YEP. WESLEY'S IN CHARGE
OF THE CHIPS.

83
00:03:53,275 --> 00:03:54,818
KETCHUP AND DILL PICKLE!

84
00:03:54,902 --> 00:03:56,195
CHIPS, GREAT.

85
00:03:56,278 --> 00:03:58,488
OKAY, GUYS, YOU'RE EXAM
IS A TAKE HOME.

86
00:03:58,572 --> 00:03:59,323
NOW I WANT YOU TO DESIGN

87
00:03:59,406 --> 00:04:00,991
AN INTERACTIVE
COMMUNITY WEBPAGE.

88
00:04:01,950 --> 00:04:03,619
YO, SPACE CADET,
WHATCHYA TYPING?

89
00:04:03,702 --> 00:04:04,995
NOTHING. IT'S PERSONAL.

90
00:04:05,078 --> 00:04:07,414
OH, LET ME SEE,
PLEASE?

91
