92
00:04:13,003 --> 00:04:15,422
WOW, CLARE,
THIS IS PRETTY STEAMY!

93
00:04:15,506 --> 00:04:16,673
I WAS JUST GOOFING AROUND.

94
00:04:16,757 --> 00:04:20,010
LIKE, WHAT IF THE GIRL
WAS THE VAMPIRE?

95
00:04:20,093 --> 00:04:23,263
THIS IS WAY BETTER THAN
THE STUFF ON FAN BOARDS.

96
00:04:23,347 --> 00:04:24,681
YOU SHOULD POST IT.

97
