104
00:04:42,491 --> 00:04:43,450
(KEYS CLACK)

105
00:04:48,789 --> 00:04:50,123
(COMPUTER BEEPS)

106
00:04:53,961 --> 00:04:55,045
HEY!

107
00:04:55,128 --> 00:04:57,339
YOU GUYS READY TO HEAR
OUR LATEST TRACK?

108
00:04:57,422 --> 00:04:58,549
OH, YOU FINISHED THE MIX?

109
00:04:58,632 --> 00:04:59,550
YEAH.

110
00:04:59,633 --> 00:05:01,593
I STAYED LATE LAST NIGHT.
NOTHING BETTER TO DO.

111
00:05:01,677 --> 00:05:02,553
HERE, LISTEN!

112
00:05:02,636 --> 00:05:05,556
JANE:
♪ HOUSE ARREST,
HOUSE ARREST ♪

113
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:07,724
♪ PUT MY RECORD TO THE TEST ♪

114
00:05:08,767 --> 00:05:11,061
♪ HOUSE ARREST,
HOUSE ARREST ♪

115
00:05:11,144 --> 00:05:13,146
WOW! THAT SOUNDS AMAZING,
SAV!

116
00:05:13,230 --> 00:05:15,941
AND TVM'S VIRAL VIDEO CONTEST
IS THIS WEEKEND!

117
00:05:16,024 --> 00:05:17,234
