I READ VAMPIRE FAN FICTION.

139
00:06:14,082 --> 00:06:16,418
MAYBE YOU SHOULD'VE CHANGED
DECLAN'S NAME TOO.

140
00:06:16,502 --> 00:06:18,086
HOLLY J:
"I TREMBLED IN ANTICIPATION,

141
00:06:18,170 --> 00:06:19,671
WANTING WHAT
I COULD NOT HAVE."

142
00:06:19,755 --> 00:06:22,257
WHO IS THIS
MADAME DEGRASSI?

143
00:06:22,341 --> 00:06:24,259
(PLAYFUL SNARL)
DELICIOUS HUMAN BLOOD!

144
00:06:24,343 --> 00:06:25,302
(LAUGHS)

145
00:06:26,428 --> 00:06:27,429
ARE YOU DONE OBSESSING,
HOLLY J?

146
00:06:27,513 --> 00:06:28,597
'CAUSE I GOT A REHEARSAL
TO RUN.

147
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,973
I'M GOING, I'M GOING.

148
00:06:31,808 --> 00:06:33,435
(EXHALES)

149
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:36,480
ALLI:
SO, HAVE YOU READ THE STORIES?

150
00:06:37,189 --> 00:06:38,815
