JUST BE A COINCIDENCE?

153
00:06:47,741 --> 00:06:48,784
COULD BE.

154
00:06:48,867 --> 00:06:50,827
BUT WHOEVER MADAME DEGRASSI IS,
SHE SURE CAN WRITE.

155
00:06:50,911 --> 00:06:53,956
GOT QUITE THE IMAGINATION,
TOO.

156
00:07:10,138 --> 00:07:11,098
UH...

157
00:07:11,974 --> 00:07:13,559
DON'T WORRY,
I CAN TAKE IT IN.

158
00:07:16,144 --> 00:07:18,021
PETER:
HEY, DUDE.

159
00:07:18,105 --> 00:07:19,690
STILL TWEAKING THE MIX?

160
00:07:19,773 --> 00:07:21,400
YEAH. KIND OF.

161
00:07:23,777 --> 00:07:24,778
NO.

162
00:07:28,031 --> 00:07:29,032
DON'T DO IT, MAN.

163
00:07:29,116 --> 00:07:32,286
WHAT?
YOU'RE TOTALLY STALKING
YOUR EX.

164
00:07:32,369 --> 00:07:33,579
MAN, IT'S NOT FAIR.

165
00:07:33,662 --> 00:07:35,539
I'M THE DUMPER,
NOT THE DUMPEE.

166
00:07:35,622 --> 00:07:38,417
SHE'S ALL HAPPY TWEETS,
AND DRIVING SCHOOL,

167
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:39,459
AND LARPING,

168
00:07:39,543 --> 00:07:41,003
AND I'M THE ONE
WHO CAN'T GET OVER IT.

169
00:07:41,086 --> 00:07:42,671
YOU ARE NOT GETTING BACK
TOGETHER WITH HER, DUDE.

170
00:07:42,754 --> 00:07:43,463
NOT AGAIN.

171
00:07:43,547 --> 00:07:45,382
I DON'T WANT TO.

172
00:07:45,465 --> 00:07:48,051
I JUST DON'T GET WHY
SHE'S HAPPY AND I'M NOT.

173
00:07:48,135 --> 00:07:49,553
WELL, IT'S 'CAUSE 
SHE'S DOING STUFF.

174
00:07:49,636 --> 00:07:51,680
IT'S ALL ABOUT DISTRACTIONS.

175
00:07:51,763 --> 00:07:53,307
YEAH, YOU'RE RIGHT.

176
00:07:53,390 --> 00:07:55,517
I'LL FIND SOMETHING.

177
00:08:01,899 --> 00:08:03,317
(EXHALES)

178
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:06,862
OKAY. I'LL TALK TO THE GUYS
ABOUT MAKING THE VIDEO.

179
00:08:06,945 --> 00:08:07,779
REALLY?

180
00:08:07,863 --> 00:08:09,531
YEAH, ONE MUSIC VIDEO
CAN'T RUIN FOUR YEARS

181
00:08:09,615 --> 00:08:10,741
OF HIGH SCHOOL, RIGHT?

182
00:08:10,824 --> 00:08:11,700
THANKS, MAN.

183
00:08:11,783 --> 00:08:13,327
WE'LL GET STARTED
SATURDAY MORNING.

184
00:08:13,410 --> 00:08:14,328
WHOA, MORNING?

185
00:08:14,411 --> 00:08:15,913
YEAH. IF WE'RE GONNA
MAKE A VIDEO,

186
00:08:15,996 --> 00:08:18,040
IT'S GOTTA BE GOOD.

187
00:08:24,046 --> 00:08:24,713
THERE YOU ARE!

188
00:08:24,796 --> 00:08:27,758
CONNOR'S E-VITE
SAID 4:30 SHARP.

189
00:08:27,841 --> 00:08:30,344
CLARE:
I THINK I'M GONNA PASS.

190
00:08:31,345 --> 00:08:34,014
MORE FORTNIGHT
FAN FICTION?

191
00:08:34,097 --> 00:08:35,516
YOU HEARD DECLAN.
HE LOVES IT.

192
00:08:35,599 --> 00:08:37,434
DECLAN IS SOMEONE ELSE'S
BOYFRIEND,

193
00:08:37,518 --> 00:08:39,394
AND IF HOLLY J KNEW
YOU WERE MADAME DEGRASSI,

194
00:08:39,478 --> 00:08:41,355
SHE'D MURDER YOU.

195
00:08:44,107 --> 00:08:46,235
IS THIS HIS SWEATER?

196
00:08:47,027 --> 00:08:48,070
I COULDN'T HELP IT.

197
00:08:48,153 --> 00:08:50,280
OKAY, YOU ARE OFFICIALLY
OBSESSED.

198
00:08:50,364 --> 00:08:51,406
TIME TO GO OUT 
IN THE DAYLIGHT

199
00:08:51,490 --> 00:08:53,116
